Mu Gu is a Dou Venerate,

31
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:05,310
while all of you are Dou Ancestors.

32
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,550
To fight the stronger enemy,

33
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:09,310
it's better

34
00:02:09,390 --> 00:02:10,470
to improve your Dou Qi.

35
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,160
Or,

36
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,270
you need to practice
a consummate technique.

37
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,640
What's wrong, Qing'er?

38
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:27,470
I was found to be helping you
without permission.

39
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:30,440
My Master withdrew my Dou Technique.

40
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:33,520
