42
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:38,920
It's OK.

43
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,280
Don't cry.

44
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:50,240
Your Dou Technique is withdrawn, so what?

45
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:56,960
You can practice this.

46
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,910
This is Demon Phoenix Bell.

47
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:03,440
Yao Chen got this gift
for refining pills for others.

48
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:06,240
It's an ancient Dou Technique
of the Heaven Demon Phoenix Tribe.

49
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,270
When practiced properly,

50
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:10,880
it can destroy all lives
within hundreds of miles.

51
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,880
You have the Heaven Demon Phoenix Bloodline,

52
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,320
while Mu Qingluan
has the Cyan Phoenix Bloodline.

53
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,600
It's fit for your practice.

54
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:25,440
What about me?

55
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,470
I said you were not in.

56
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,720
Are there any tips
for learning this Dou Technique?

57
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,560
There's just one thing.

58
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,520
This unique Dou Technique is brutal.

59
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,600
Effeminate people can't learn it.

60
00:03:47,550 --> 00:03:48,830
I'm not effeminate.

61
