from sealing Magic Poison Spot.

67
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,270
But the supreme Yang Qi is still the best.

68
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:59,110
You'll die from trying to make a breakthrough

69
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,600
with the supreme Yang Qi.

70
00:05:01,230 --> 00:05:02,510
To reach the Dou Venerate level,

71
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,510
I'd like to take all the risks.

72
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,280
Shh.

73
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,320
Stop! Stop!

74
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:39,350
Stay right there!

75
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,480
Junior Master.

76
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,760
Junior Master.

77
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:43,320
She… This spoiled Zi Yan

78
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,040
stole our elixirs and hit me.

79
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,720
Look how seriously I was beaten.

80
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:48,440
She took all my food away as well.

81
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,830
Did you see where she was going?

82
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,390
I must catch her tonight.

83
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:53,160
Otherwise, no meal for all!

84
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,440
Don't run!

85
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,350
Freeze!

86
00:05:58,790 --> 00:06:00,070
Stay right there!

87
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:52,000
Isn't there anything I can practice?

88
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,880
No, there isn't.

89
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,640
Little Candle, I'm not eating.

90
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:06,910
Take it back.

91
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:15,830
Someone is not eating properly.

92
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,190
Xun'er!

93
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,760
Xun'er, what brings you here?

94
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:25,320
If you eat properly,

95
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,790
I can consider staying here longer.

96
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,880
OK.

97
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,950
As you order.

98
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,230
Put me down.

99
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,480
No.

100
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:34,670
I want

101
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,000
to hug you more.

102
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,270
Slow down. They're all yours.

103
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,480
Be careful not to choke.

104
00:07:45,670 --> 00:07:47,720
There is no one on my way here.

105
00:07:47,790 --> 00:07:48,630
