108
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,040
Days later, we'll fight the Hall of Souls.

109
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,790
They are all practicing diligently.

110
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:57,630
Great!

111
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:59,000
I'm here at the right time.

112
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,880
Look what treasure I bring to you.

113
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,390
Xun'er, you do find it!

114
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,790
This belongs to the Xiao Family.

115
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,640
I'm now returning it to its owner.

116
00:08:11,570 --> 00:08:12,420
With it,

117
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:14,640
you're sure to develop your killer skill

118
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,480
before fighting the Hall of Souls.

119
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,110
Here's some food for you.

120
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,080
It's Xiao Yan's favorite.

121
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:47,070
Have a taste.

122
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,480
How's it?

123
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,470
No wonder Xiao Yan likes it.

124
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:07,510
Little Fairy Doctor,

125
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:13,150
are you into Xiao Yan deep in your heart?

126
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:23,350
What's Xiao Yan like

127
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,440
in your mind?

128
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:35,550
Xiao Yan

129
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:38,030
is the same as his Heavenly Flames.

130
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:40,640
He can bring warmth and hope

131
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,840
to those around him.

132
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:47,360
What about you?

133
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,350
What do you think of Xiao Yan?

134
00:09:53,110 --> 00:09:53,950
He…

135
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,520
He's always reckless.

136
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:58,840
He tends to act on impulse.

137
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:01,230
He always gets others worried.

138
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:06,790
But he never lets others down.

139
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,160
Yeah.

140
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,790
He never lets others down.

141
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:15,630
So,

142
00:10:16,350 --> 00:10:17,190
you admit.

143
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,480
Admit what?

144
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,350
You admit that you're into him

145
00:10:21,710 --> 00:10:23,110
deep in your heart.

146
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,640
When my Woeful Poison Body
was about to erupt,

147
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,470
I was widely disgusted.

148
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:39,590
There was this unexpected fellow

149
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:43,910
running into my world
and standing before me

150
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:47,110
to bear all the unfriendliness for me.

151
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:51,320
From then on,

152
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,230
he has been there.

153
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,080
Like…

154
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,280
I think

155
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:05,910
there's nothing wrong

156
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,280
with me liking a person.

157
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:13,790
I'll bury my feelings deep in my heart

158
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:18,030
and accompany him forever.

159
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:22,320
I want to repay his help with my life.

160
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,710
Oh, here you are.

161
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:39,990
Heavenly Poison Encyclopedia?

162
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:42,840
Made by Heavenly Poison Saint centuries ago,

163
00:11:43,470 --> 00:11:45,350
it contains numerous ways to refine poisons.

164
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:51,030
Even Dou Venerates can be killed silently.

165
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,840
It's said it has disappeared.

166
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:55,910
Where did you get it?

167
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:59,080
For these years, Gu Clan has been collecting

168
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,000
Qi Methods, Dou Techniques and records

169
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:03,350
that have gone lost on the Continent.

170
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:06,110
I've read it through.

171
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:08,280
It requires the practitioner

172
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:09,960
to have excellent talent and skills

173
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,950
regarding the use and makeup of poisons.

174
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:12,990
It suits you well.

175
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,320
Thank you, Xun'er.

176
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:21,150
Actually, I've got another question.

177
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,960
Is Xiao Yan bothered by anything?

178
00:12:27,470 --> 00:12:28,760
I've taken from Gu Clan

179
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:31,470
the second volume
of Heavenly Flame Triple Xuan Change.

180
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:35,350
He was just not as excited as he used to be

181
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:36,480
when he got Qi Methods.

182
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:39,440
The fight against the Hall of Souls is coming,

183
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:40,590
but he's not out for practice.

184
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:43,080
Instead, he locks himself inside the room.

185
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,230
This is just not his style.

186
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:47,590
What happened?

187
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:50,910
Mu Gu spread Magic Poison Spot on him.

188
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,470
He can't use Heavenly Flames now.

189
00:12:53,110 --> 00:12:55,710
Wind Sage said he's not in the fight.

190
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:57,670
He can't use Heavenly Flames?

191
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,120
Oh, no!

192
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,880
(Heavenly Flame Triple Xuan Change)

193
00:13:15,550 --> 00:13:16,760
(relies on magic skills)

194
00:13:16,790 --> 00:13:18,320
(to mobilize the inside Heavenly Flames out)

195
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,150
(and improve one's strength exponentially.)

196
00:13:22,110 --> 00:13:23,440
(The fighting capacity)

197
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:25,080
(can be increased by three levels instantly)

198
00:13:25,470 --> 00:13:27,280
(if its three Changes are achieved together.)

199
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:42,640
Green Lotus Change.

200
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:46,920
Fallen Change.

201
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:25,280
I know you couldn't help but practice it.

202
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:32,640
Should you use Heavenly Flames,

203
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,580
before you arrive at the Hall of Souls,

204
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:36,110
you would die from a poison explosion.

205
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,790
They all take the risk and try their best,

206
00:14:40,470 --> 00:14:41,590
while I can't do anything.

207
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:43,280
It feels painful to me.

208
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:45,670
There's something you can do.

209
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:55,230
What's this?

210
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:57,410
Flame Lotus Bottle.

211
00:14:58,410 --> 00:15:00,160
The reason why Yao Chen
repulsed the Hall of Souls

212
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:01,550
with Bone Spirit Cold Flame by himself

213
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,080
is because of this bottle.

214
00:15:04,110 --> 00:15:06,320
Made by Dou Technique of fire attribute,

215
00:15:06,470 --> 00:15:07,880
it can store a pinch of Heavenly Flame.

216
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:10,960
When kindled by Dou Qi in fights,

217
00:15:11,350 --> 00:15:13,370
the flame can produce great explosive power.

218
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:15,110
Without Heavenly Flame,

219
00:15:15,470 --> 00:15:17,440
you can still fight
Honored Elders of the Hall of Souls.

220
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:23,530
Dou Qi Continent values
Heavenly Flames the most.

221
00:15:23,590 --> 00:15:25,300
What represses the Hall of Souls' evil skills

222
00:15:25,470 --> 00:15:26,310
is Heavenly Flame.

223
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:29,110
Your unique weapon is also Heavenly Flame.

224
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:31,760
You're meant to fight the Hall of Souls.

225
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:43,000
It's such a useful method.

226
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,960
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

227
00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:46,520
I…

228
00:15:46,550 --> 00:15:47,520
I forgot. Acceptable?

229
00:15:58,520 --> 00:15:59,360
One more.

230
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:10,000
No matter how little the pinch is,

231
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,970
it will trigger your Magic Poison Spot.

232
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,920
I know.

233
00:16:15,350 --> 00:16:17,280
I can handle myself.

234
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,030
See you later, Wind Sage.

235
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:32,110
The bottles have not been used for 50 years.

236
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,000
No one knows if they are useful.

237
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:37,600
Yao Chen,

238
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,320
I hope

239
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:41,030
your bottles still function well.

240
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,590
Wind Sage has said

241
00:16:59,470 --> 00:17:01,230
you shouldn't keep filling the bottles.

242
00:17:02,230 --> 00:17:04,070
You can't use your Heavenly Flame so often.

243
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:05,710
Have a rest.

244
00:17:07,950 --> 00:17:09,350
OK. I got it.

245
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:19,120
Xun'er,

246
00:17:19,230 --> 00:17:21,400
how do you know that?

247
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,920
Well, how do I get to know?

248
00:17:26,470 --> 00:17:28,000
Anyway, you didn't tell me.

249
00:17:29,190 --> 00:17:30,830
Everyone in Starfall Hall knows,

250
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:32,430
except for me.

251
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:33,600
No.

252
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,950
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

253
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:37,520
It's just because

254
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:39,110
I hate to make you sad.

255
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,230
How long did you try to keep it hidden?

256
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:43,310
A day?

257
00:17:43,950 --> 00:17:44,790
Half a month?

258
00:17:46,950 --> 00:17:48,880
But how could you keep it from me

259
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:50,640
if you want me to stay?

260
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:53,350
Or,

261
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,310
from the beginning,

262
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:57,110
were you expecting me to go back

263
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,710
and trying to keep it up for a day?

264
00:17:59,710 --> 00:18:01,280
No, no. I…

265
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,280
I don't want you to leave.

266
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:05,350
Could you stay here?

267
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:08,240
I was…

268
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:11,430
I didn't want you to feel sad for me.

269
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:19,350
Xiao Yan, could you promise to me

270
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:21,760
that you will tell me everything

271
00:18:22,230 --> 00:18:23,880
no matter what you encounter.

272
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:27,880
Be it good or bad news,

273
00:18:28,430 --> 00:18:29,920
I will be by your side.

274
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:34,430
In both bitter and sweet times,

275
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:37,640
I will share what you're going through.

276
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:41,150
OK.

277
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,190
I promise.

278
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:48,640
These bottles are for emergencies.

279
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:54,000
